The person is a 22-year-old female who identifies herself as White. She has been arrested 1 time and has been convicted. She is 5 feet 7 inches and weighs 145 lbs. She has never been married and is currently living alone. She has a high school diploma and is enrolled in a 4-year college. She has held 3 jobs during the year. She has used drugs in the past four years (marijuana) and has not felt depressed over the past month.
